gems.name: google-cloud-data_catalog-v1
gems.info: DataCatalog is a centralized and unified data catalog service for all your Cloud resources, where users and systems can discover data, explore and curate its semantics, understand how to act on it, and help govern its usage. Note that google-cloud-data_catalog-v1 is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-data_catalog instead. See the readme for more details.
